<BaseLayout
  title="Discordium.org – Harassment, Doxxing, Predators, Privacy Violations & Misconduct"
  description="Report on Discordium.org covering harassment, GDPR concerns, doxxing allegations, admittance to predatory and illegal behavior, and Discord TOS violations."
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
      Discordium.org: What’s Actually Going On?
    </h1>

    <p class="mb-4">
      Discordium presents itself as a professional Discord advertising network.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 font-semibold">
      Multiple reports suggest a different reality.
    </p>

    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-6">
      <li>Harassment, threats, intimidation, and retaliation against critics</li>
      <li>Non-consensual sharing of personal information</li>
      <li>Attempts to suppress reports and reviews</li>
      <li>Openly admitting to predators and illegal behavior</li>
      <li>Copyright concerns and DMCA violations</li>
      <li>Conflicting claims about GDPR compliance</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      This site documents both publicly available evidence and testimonies.
    </p>
